1
00:00:00,500 --> 00:00:03,000
There's nothing wrong
with the radio.

2
00:00:03,500 --> 00:00:06,000
It must have been
a station.

3
00:00:15,500 --> 00:00:18,500
Well, there's no one
around here.

4
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:31,000
It's late. You've
gotten up earlier.

5
00:00:31,500 --> 00:00:34,500
I already lost a whole hour of sleep on this.

6
00:00:36,900 --> 00:00:37,700
There it is.

7
00:00:50,500 --> 00:00:53,500
I wonder what happened
to last year's.

8
00:00:54,000 --> 00:00:57,000
Each year we spend
good money on these.

9
00:00:57,500 --> 00:01:00,500
We drive all the way out
and it's vanished.

10
00:01:03,500 --> 00:01:06,500
wind rushes through
the bare trees

11
00:01:32,500 --> 00:01:35,000
Church was this
morning, remember?

12
00:01:59,000 --> 00:02:02,000
I haven't seen you
in church lately.

13
00:02:32,600 --> 00:02:35,000
They're coming to get
you, Barbara.

14
00:02:38,600 --> 00:02:41,000
Stop it. You're
ignorant.

15
00:02:43,800 --> 00:02:46,500
Stop it. You're acting
like a child.

16
00:02:48,600 --> 00:02:49,600
Look here comes one of them right now, come on hurry.
